---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="The Road Gets Harder: Trucking Industry Challenges 2026 | Community Spotlight"
  description="A deep dive into the challenges facing the trucking industry in 2026 and a spotlight on local Shelby business F&S Expedited LLC."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-orange-500/20 bg-orange-500/5">
          <span class="text-orange-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Community Spotlight</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/30"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-sky/60 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #1 Article #7 • May 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          The Road Gets Harder: <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-red-500">What Today's Trucking Companies Are Up Against</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto italic">
          "If you bought it, a truck brought it."
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-3xl mb-16 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/20 to-transparent opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
           <span class="text-brand-sky/20 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transform -rotate-12 text-center px-4">Shelby Web Company <br/> Community Spotlight</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-sky/90 mb-12">
          Featured on <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline decoration-brand-cyan/30 underline-offset-4">Shelby Web Company</a> | Spotlighting <strong>F&S Expedited LLC</strong>
        </p>

        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">
          The trucking industry is navigating one of the most difficult stretches in recent memory—a perfect storm of rising fuel costs, relentless operating expenses, trade policy turbulence, and a freight market that's been grinding through a prolonged downturn since 2022. And yet, hauling companies like <strong>F&S Expedited</strong> keep showing up. Every day. Because the job still has to get done.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-orange-500">01.</span> A Freight Recession Nobody Saw Coming (Or Ending)
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/90 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Most people outside the industry don't realize it, but trucking has been living through what analysts are calling the "Great Freight Recession." It didn't start with a dramatic crash. It crept in quietly: too many trucks chasing too little freight, and rates that barely covered costs.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Numbers Tell a Sobering Story</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 list-none p-0">
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">•</span>
              <p class="text-brand-sky/70 m-0">Industry revenues fell from $1 trillion in 2023 to $906 billion in 2024</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">•</span>
              <p class="text-brand-sky/70 m-0">Thousands of small carriers have exited the market entirely</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">•</span>
              <p class="text-brand-sky/70 m-0">Carrier authority revocations surged to over 6,400 in a single month in late 2025</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-orange-500">02.</span> Fuel: The Number That Never Cooperates
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/90 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Fuel alone represents 20–30% of total operating costs. For small hauling operations, there's no hedge fund or corporate treasury to absorb the shock. It comes straight out of the owner's pocket.
        </p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2">$4.60</div>
            <div class="text-orange-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Average Diesel / Gal</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2">30%</div>
            <div class="text-orange-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Operating Cost Impact</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-orange-500">03.</span> Why Companies Like F&S Expedited LLC Are Genuinely Valuable Right Now
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/90 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          F&S Expedited LLC, serving Shelby, NC and the surrounding 100-mile radius, is one of those companies. Fully licensed and insured, operating a modern fleet, and offering everything from gravel and material delivery to emergency expedited hauling and debris removal—they've built their reputation the hard way.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/10 to-transparent border border-orange-500/20 p-8 my-12 rounded-3xl">
          <p class="text-white font-medium italic mb-6">"When you hire a hauling company today, you're not just paying for a truck and a driver. You're supporting a business that absorbed every fuel spike, every insurance increase, every regulatory headache—and kept their commitment anyway."</p>
          <p class="text-orange-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">— Shelby Web Company Community Spotlight</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8">What You Can Do</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-12">If you have a project that needs hauling—gravel delivery, land clearing, debris removal, construction materials, or emergency services—choose a local carrier who is invested in this community.</p>

        <!-- Spotlight CTA Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-600 to-brand-darkest p-12 rounded-[2rem] text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(255,165,0,0.1),transparent_70%)]"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 relative z-10 text-center">Support Local: F&S Expedited LLC</h2>
          
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 relative z-10">
            <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-md p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
              <div class="text-orange-400 font-bold mb-1">Joe</div>
              <a href="tel:8653649011" class="text-white text-xl font-black hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">(865) 364-9011</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-md p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
              <div class="text-orange-400 font-bold mb-1">Luke</div>
              <a href="tel:7047518141" class="text-white text-xl font-black hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">(704) 751-8141</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
            <a href="https://www.fs-expeditedllc.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white text-orange-600 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-orange-50 transition-all">
              Visit Website
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-8 relative z-10">
             Serving Shelby, NC and a 100-mile radius.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-24 p-8 bg-brand-dark/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl">
          <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm mb-0">
            This article was written and published by <strong>Shelby Web Company</strong> as part of an ongoing series spotlighting local businesses. To learn more about our web design and digital marketing services, visit <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline">www.shelbywebco.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer navigation -->
      <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">About Us</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
